reviewText:
Episodes on this disc from Quality are:

05 Akim the Terrible
10 The Return of the Androids
17 The Lure of Light
19 The Race Against Time
21 The Brain Machine
25 The Forbidden Experiment
36 Deadline at Noon
39 The Subworld Revenge

I love this series but given the overlap in the episodes from one public domain release of this series to the next, it would be extremely useful to know which episodes are on this DVD before deciding whether to buy it.
This show was done in Europe. I watched as a kid, compared to today's shows, it seems very silly, but I really enjoyed it.
